_sText:
jb_clouds is a port of the jb_clouds map from the Counter-Strike: Global Offensive game.

**Jail Break Map** Terrorists are prisoners and have to kill all the Guards. 

CTs have to guard them and by legal means try to lower their numbers. 

**Info:** - Completly new Jailbreak experience: _revolution in gameplay_ for both, CTs & T **Features:** - Football/Soccer with working ball - Basketball - Swimming Pool with a Slide - Jump Rope with 3 speed settings - Tic-Tac-Toe - Roulette - Climb (Easy/Hard/Extreme) - Bomb Toss - Zombie Freeday - Hospital - Colors - Tower Jump - Bunnyhop - Surf - Volleyball - War/Gang Area - Disco with 6 Songs - Minigame random chooser - Weapon Spawners in the Armory for your skins - Many Secrets ;)
